text: Thank you! I just checked them out

Does anybody else have more than one moment? Like most of the time, we have fun in a way that I know we are friends. But then some little voice inside me hints at the possibility that I might see him as something more. And it just happens more and more often. Maybe that means I haven’t gotten there yet. But man, I miss having a crush.
I would rather you did, than hear that you hurt yourself. Take care friend! :)
